Commentary Text: Murugan Ashwin to Samson, 2 runs, wow! That's a stunning effort in the deep. A half-tracker and Samson rocked back to pull. Pooran, at deep mid-wicket, leaps full length over the rope to collect the ball. He was stretching to the maximum possible, caught that actually with the left hand. And, a millisecond before falling onto the ground, he flicks the ball back into play. What presence of mind when he was horizontal to the ground! "That's the best I have seen," says KP on air. Acrobatic save! Just brilliant
